Sentencas: Segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells (SIS-SOFC) have been stacked on all sides of a porous ceramic support using decalcomania method.
Titulo: Effect of cell length on the performance of segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells fabricated using decalcomania method

Sentencas: When cells are stacked using decalcomania method, the cell components do not penetrate into the porous support or neighboring layers, resulting in excellent interfacial bonding.
Titulo: Effect of cell length on the performance of segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells fabricated using decalcomania method

Sentencas: The cell components formed uniform thickness as well.
Titulo: Effect of cell length on the performance of segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells fabricated using decalcomania method

Sentencas: Since the current flows laterally in SIS-SOFC, the cells are prepared having dimensions of 8 and 5 mm in length to minimize their lateral resistance.
Titulo: Effect of cell length on the performance of segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells fabricated using decalcomania method

Sentencas: Subsequent power output characteristics have been studied.
Titulo: Effect of cell length on the performance of segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells fabricated using decalcomania method

Sentencas: As cell length decrease from 8 to 5 mm, the open circuit voltage and maximum power density increase.
Titulo: Effect of cell length on the performance of segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells fabricated using decalcomania method

Sentencas: This is attributed to the lower lateral resistance due to shorter current path.
Titulo: Effect of cell length on the performance of segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells fabricated using decalcomania method

Sentencas: Impedance analysis also shows that ohmic resistances decrease substantially with decreasing cell length.
Titulo: Effect of cell length on the performance of segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells fabricated using decalcomania method
